p bar, however i have been in 3 tank groups where ive thrown a garrote, pulled aggro, and either a: Hoarfrosted 3 times to detaunt w/o ever losing aggro or b: stoping attack completley.<br>
<br>
Now during the a: event either the tanks were not taunting the mob or something was really weird with aggro.<br>
<br>
b: situation becomes an issue when the group sees you attack once or twice per mob, then never attack again-if im going to do that why have me eh?<br>
<br>
So anyway I know about aggro control.<br>
<br>
The main problem is that we bring NOTHING to a group that makes us wanted.<br>
If you want a damage dealer, get a tank or nuker<br>
you want meat shield? get a tank<br>
High damage/debuffs? Nukers<br>
Longrange? Heh...<br>
<br>
I dont know if im asking for new skills or what hehe I just want something that will actually make us wanted in exp groups, in RvR groups (battlegrounds only so far) I have plenty of invites to group, and have saved so many healers for my realm its not funny, id just like to see this translated somehow to the &quot;normal&quot; game.<br>
