<br>
A funny story about groups.<br>
<br>
The other day I went to Darkness Falls, we did not have access and a group out front was talking about a raid to take a keep. They where asking for stealthers to help on the raid. I agreed to go help on the keep raid. The group was talking all through the keep raid how we would stay a group when we go back to DF. So we get other people together go on the keep raid, go back to DF, get inside DF. They then tell me, thanks for the help on the raid and booted me out of the group. <br>
<br>
Gee thanks! hehe.<br>
