 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/umeleth.showPublicProfile?language=EN>meleth</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/17/02 3:13:51 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2804.topic&index=15>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Not getting into any groups</span><hr size=1> I had the same problems up until level 25. Then i started organizing my own groups. Instead of trying to join one i use /who like a madman and send the people i want to join the group msgs. This way i will also be able to handpick the classes i want in the group so i get a good group. And when you have a good group going people will come back. Add the ppl that you like to group with to your friends list so you can see if they're on.  I'm 40 now and i get tells all the time asking if i have a group going and if there are any slots in it. Now i even get invited into groups cause they will have ppl in them who has grouped with me before and done good.<br>
<br>
Sure we don't have it as easy as all the other classes to get groups, but it is doable if we put some work into it. Also sending out a msg saying something like 'Hi, i'm a 29Infiltrator want to group?' is probably not that smart. Start with something like 'Hey, we're pulling together a group to kill gobs (Or whatever you're hunting) and we got a spot open for a &lt;insert class&gt; if you're interested.'<br>
<br>
Try it, you'll be amazed. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showPrevMessage?topicID=2804.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showNextMessage?topicID=2804.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2804.topic&index=15><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/reply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.emailToFriend?topicID=2804.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.threadControl?topicID=2804.topic><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/dagger.jpg border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=2804.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=2804.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub35.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion">Main Lounge<option value="thesafehousecontractsbountiesjobsquestsetc">News Bulletin<option value="thesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies">Training Studio<option value="thesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers">The Back Alley<option value="thesafehousefr